      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-mrl5",
      "rationale": "Solver (OpenFOAM v9) is under ISO 9001-certified quality management. Version-controlled source at tagged release; regression test suite of 412 cases passes at CI/CD gate. Independent code review completed by third-party auditor. SQA plan documented and traceable to IEC 62304 software lifecycle requirements for Class III medical device context."
