      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/code-verification-mrl5",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the full Navier-Stokes plus power-law hemolysis transport system. Observed order of accuracy p = 1.97 (theoretical 2nd order); error norms confirm implementation correctness for all governing equations including the scalar hemolysis transport equation. Results archived in verification report VR-CODE-2025-03."
